{"examples":[{"conversion_notes":"The Python helper function is represented as a Jac ability declared with def. The loop and accumulator stay explicit, but Jac uses braces and semicolons rather than Python indentation.","jac_code":"def sum_even(nums: list[int]) -> int {
    total = 0;
    for n in nums {
        if n % 2 == 0 {
            total = total + n;
        }
    }
