"},{"conversion_notes":"The Python dictionary frequency counter is converted to a typed Jac ability. The dictionary update logic is preserved, while the syntax follows Jac block and statement rules.","jac_code":"def count_letters(text: str) -> dict[str, int] {
    counts = {};
