"},{"conversion_notes":"The Python recursive factorial function becomes a Jac def ability with explicit type annotations. The base case and recursive step are preserved directly.","jac_code":"def factorial(n: int) -> int {
    if n <= 1 {
        return 1;
    }
    return n * factorial(n - 1);
}
","python_code":"def factorial(n):
